    "g, Dot plot showing the top 10 significantly enriched Gene Ontology biological process terms of the positively correlated genes of C23 with clusterProfiler.",
    "Data were analyzed using a one-sided Fisher's exact test, and P values were adjusted using the Benjamini-Hochberg method.",
    "h, UMAP visualization of the biological states obtained by cross-tissue reciprocal reference mapping between the PBMC atlas reference and the BMMC query dataset.",
    "The BMMC cells are colored by cell types transferred from the PBMC atlas using MIDAS (left) and by cell types annotated with Seurat (right).",
    "i, Confusion plot showing the label transfer consistency in a crosstissue label transfer task on the BMMC mosaic dataset."
